com.compendium.core.datamodel
Interface INodePosition

All Superinterfaces:
ICoreConstants, IPCObject, java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
NodePosition
public interface INodePosition
extends IPCObject

The INodePosition object defines the position of a node in a view. The position is defined by an X and Y coordinate in the view's relative coordinate system.
